item.title: What is this?
item.dc:creator: @framexile framexile
item.description:
@framexile wrote:

client.java:8520: error: exception IOException is never thrown in body of corresponding try statement } catch (IOException ioexception) {

client.java:8520 means in client.java line 8520 the error is posted. Can’t help you with it, but if you didn’t know about that. It can be helpful, just mess around with it and maybe you can get it, good luck. Notepad++ is really helpful for this. I recommend it
